LAMP: linux + apache(nginx) + mysql + php

LAMP install : sudo apt-get install apache2 php5 mysql-server php5-mysql

introduction:
    apache2:
        apache is a open source web server

    php5:
        php:

    mysql-server:

    php5-mysql:

LAMP process:
    browser convert URL to IP address that via DNS -->  send browser request to php -->  php parse --> mysql data exechange



php extension package : (sudo apt-get install php5-gd curl libcurl3 libcurl3-dev php5-curl)


LAMP install --> filezilla install --> ssh service install --> shh service restart --> 
logging filezilla succed

mysql corel configuration is my.cnf
php corel configuration is php.ini
